<plot>Concept by Dan Jansen, Mirror Man is a story about a young man, Vincent, whose life becomes complex after his mother's death. Vincent finds that the only way to endure his loss is to look at the world through reflections in mirrors "Mirror Man is a story of a young man's fear, repression, and denial. The irony is that Vincent, unlike most of us, is not troubled or embarrassed by his fears; he owns them and does not apologize for them."</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?371570</url></doc>
